headline: Rocket Lab, Micron, And CoreWeave Are Among the Top 10 Large-Cap Gainers Last Week (Dec. 22-Dec. 26): Are the Others in Your Portfolio?
summary: These ten large-cap stocks were top performers last week. Are they a part of your portfolio? Rocket Lab Corporation (NASDAQ:RKLB) gained 15.5% this week after the company announced it launched its 21st Electron rocket of the year to deploy the latest satellite to space for multi-launch customer Institute for Q-shu Pioneers of Space. Also, Needham analyst Ryan Koontz maintained a Buy rating, raising the price forecast from $63 to $90. Lumentum Holdings Inc. (NASDAQ:LITE) gained 14.76% this week B
